title: Local.Kung.Fu.2. WEB-DL.x265.[TEAM-SB]
description:
Local KungFu 2 is an Assamese Kung fu action comedy film. It is directed by Kenny Basumatary and produced by Durlov Baruah. It is the sequel to 2013 film Local Kung Fu.[1][2] The sequel is based on William Shakespeare's The Comedy of Errors. The film-makers successfully raised money for post-production through crowdfunding[3] and the film was released on 19 April 2017.
